{%- comment -%}
  Reusable "Log in to see pricing" CTA. Renders wherever a price
  would normally render for logged-out visitors. Keeps the wording
  and link target consistent across card, PDP, search, cart, etc.

  The CTA includes a `return_url` query param so the buyer lands
  back on the page they came from after authenticating. Shopify's
  account login flow honours `return_url` natively. We pass only
  `request.path` (path-only, no scheme) to avoid an open-redirect
  vulnerability — `request.path` is already path-only on Shopify
  but we URL-encode it as defence in depth.

  Inputs (optional):
    - block_modifier : 'small' | '' (default '')
                       'small' renders a smaller version for tight
                       slots like search autocomplete results.
{%- endcomment -%}
<a
  href="{{ routes.account_login_url }}?return_url={{ request.path | url_encode }}"
  class="misc-price-cta{% if block_modifier == 'small' %} misc-price-cta--small{% endif %}"
>
  Log in to see pricing
</a>
